name: Opening Ceremonies
description: Do you bleed black or gold? Head here to find out!

name: Closing Ceremonies
description: Come see how you and your friends did! Will Black or Gold take the crown?

name: Canadian Ninja Warrior
description: Climb and slide your way through our inflatable obstacle course to battle for points!

name: Ultimeate Frisbee
description: A timeless classic where you can run, jump and catch your way to victory for your team

name: Doc-u-short Festival
description: Don't just watch documentaries on Netflix—make one yourself! Direct, produce & film your own short documentary with a surprise topic.

name: Lipsyncing
description: Unleash your inner rockstar in the Science Teaching Complex.

name: Lions Lair
description: It's Dragon Den-- UW-style! Design your idea and pitch it to a panel of entrepreneurs with help from Waterloo's entrepreneurial ecosystem.

name: Boat Building
description: All aboard! Can you build a boat fit for the sea?

name: Capture the Calculus
description: Have YOU studied? No? That's okay! Come help your team find X(am)!

name: Geocashing
description: Are you ready to Cache-in some points? Learn about Geocaching and win some points for your team!

name: Escape Rooms
description: Legends say those who find themselves in the University of Underloo never return. Will you escape to tell the tale?

name: Reaction Rocketeering
description: How far can you launch a rocket filled with vinegar and baking soda? Create the perfect formula to see!

name: Human Checkers
description: Tacticians and Strategists unite in a game of lifesized checkers! Work together to win and earn points for your team!

name: Coffee Run
description: It's important to be highly caffeinated as a UWaterloo student, so come out for this fast paced iNews sponsored event!

name: Sardines
description: They say the Psychology, Anthropology & Sociology building was built to be complex and twisty like a brain—will you find the leaders hidden within?

name: Human Knot
description: Get your team into a mess of your own making and use your brains & teamwork to get yourselves out!

name: Human Bingo
description: B-I-N-G-O is not how you spell the names of the new friends you'll meet in this activity!

name: Elf, Goblins, Wizards
description: #teamelf, #teamgoblin, or #teamwizard? Pick one and face off in the biggest magical war of the century.

name: Huckle Buckle
description: High intensity test of your new found friendships!
